    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The 6 non-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out per ASME V&V 40 Table 3 at MRL 2. Benchmark validation demonstrates RH index prediction error of 4.2% NRMSE, well within the 15% acceptance criterion. Grid convergence confirmed at GCI < 2%. The model is judged fit for purpose to identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
